+/// CR 113.1a + CR 611.2: Parse "gain[s] all activated abilities of <donor>
+/// [until end of turn]" (Quicksilver Elemental, Grell Philosopher) into
+/// `Effect::GainActivatedAbilitiesOfTarget`. The fixed lead-in phrase is
